caption.p: Protection Against A/Nanchang/1/99 sublethal challenge. Mice were immunized with either 10 8 or 10 10 virus particles of recombinant Ad5-Mosaic, Ad5-A/PR/8/34, Ad5-Pdm09, 600 ng Fluzone, or PBS and challenged with 10 3.6 TCID 50 equivalents of mouse-adapted A/Nanchang/1/99 virus three weeks later ( n = 5). Mice were monitored daily and humanely euthanized if 25% weight loss was recorded. ( A, B) Weight loss for individual mice and ( C, D) average weight loss are reported (data for average weight loss is reported as the mean with standard error).
